Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.74,0:00:05.60,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,mini戰國basara2
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.23,0:00:11.56,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大意！！月夜的片倉君
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.47,0:00:19.69,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來沒人趁著夜色逃跑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.47,0:01:05.09,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣子看來…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.74,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人趁著黑夜來偷菜！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.57,0:01:11.54,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.35,0:01:18.03,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是…前田家的浪子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.35,0:01:20.76,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 你也來散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.00,0:01:24.82,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚月亮不錯 心情真舒爽呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.42,0:01:30.09,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在伊達領地的中心散步？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.23,0:01:33.14,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就放你一馬 不過把偷走的都給我還回來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.28,0:01:35.31,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誒 偷走的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.41,0:01:37.60,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是要裝傻裝到底？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.89,0:01:39.71,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 等一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.83,0:01:41.94,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可什麼都沒偷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.16,0:01:46.66,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的真的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.56,0:01:58.67,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,切 膽子真夠大的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.80,0:02:00.48,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不偷走 直接吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.64,0:02:01.94,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道是慣犯？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:04.36,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都說了不是我嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.52,0:02:05.64,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來 
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:07.59,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼小的牙印
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.79,0:02:09.63,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼看都是小孩子吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.89,0:02:11.89,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他抓住好好教訓一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.03,0:02:14.29,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想看看他父母是長什麼樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.61,0:02:16.55,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.39,0:02:23.55,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夢吉…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.63,0:02:26.01,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來是你小子…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.47,0:02:32.24,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.62,0:02:40.95,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.32,0:02:43.04,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年收成不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.86,0:02:47.55,katakura,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好愛護它哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.44,0:02:54.92,maeda,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
